cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper describes a neural network-based approach for automated segmentation of brain tumors from 3D MRIs. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the use of an autoencoder for regularization, which could also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
